 environment variable on the conductor node is used. You must specify the same value for this property in all of the DB2 Connector stages in the job.\" label=\"Instance\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"Instance\" required=\"false\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"string\"/><Property callout=\"getList\" calloutDescription=\"Lists the detected databases. The value for the Instance property does not affect the databases that are detected. The list includes only the databases for the currently configured, active DB2 instance in the DB2 Connector environment.\" calloutLabel=\"Database\" calloutType=\"enumerator\" description=\"Specifies the name of the database/location to connect to for running parallel jobs and on the conductor node. If not specified, the default database/location for the active instance on the conductor node is used (specified through the DB2DBDFT DB2 registry variable).\" label=\"Database/Location\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"Database\" required=\"true\" type=\"string\" xsi:type=\"asc:CalloutProperty\"><CalloutArgument name=\"class\">Databases</CalloutArgument></Property><Property description=\"Specifies the user name to use for connecting to the database for running parallel jobs and on the conductor node.\" label=\"User name\" maxLength=\"256\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minLength=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"Username\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the password to use for connecting to the database for running parallel jobs and on the conductor node.\" label=\"Password\" maxLength=\"256\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minLength=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"Password\" required=\"false\" type=\"protectedstring\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the full path to the DB2 client library file on the conductor node. If not specified, the system default library name for the currently configured DB2 environment is used.\" label=\"DB2 client library file\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"DB2ClientLibFile\