mma</Value></Property></Property></Property><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Before/After SQL properties\" filterChildPropertiesOnValue=\"true\" label=\"Before/After SQL\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"BeforeAfter\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"><Property default=\"\" description=\"Enter the SQL statement or the fully-qualified name of the file that contains the SQL statement to run once before any data is processed.\" label=\"Before SQL\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" multiline=\"true\" name=\"before\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Select Yes to read the SQL statement from the file that is specified in the Before SQL statement property.\" label=\"Read Before SQL statement from file\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"ReadFromFileBeforeSQL\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"true\" description=\"Abort the job if there is an error executing a command\" label=\"Fail on error\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"FailOnError\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/></Property><Property default=\"\" description=\"Enter the SQL statement or the fully-qualified name of the file that contains the SQL statement to run once after all data is processed.\" label=\"After SQL\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" multiline=\"true\" name=\"after\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Select Yes to read the SQL statement from the file that is specified in the After SQL statement property.\" label=\"Read After SQL statement from file\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"ReadFromFileAfterSQL\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"true\" description=\"Abort the job if there is an error executing a command\" label=\"Fail on error\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"FailOnError\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/></Property><Property default=\"\" description=\"Enter the SQL statement or the fully-qualified name of the file that contains the SQL statement to run once on each node before any data is processed on that node.\" engines=\"ee\" label=\"Before SQL (node)\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" multiline=\"true\" name=\"beforeNode\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Select Yes to read the SQL statement from the file that is specified in the Before SQL (node) statement property.\" label=\"Read Before SQL (node) statement from file\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"ReadFromFileBeforeSQLNode\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"true\" description=\"Abort the job if there is an error executing a command\" label=\"Fail on error\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"FailOnError\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/></Property><Property default=\"\" description=\"Enter the SQL statement or the fully-qualified name of the file that contains the SQL statement to run once one each node after all data is processed on that node.\" engines=\"ee\" label=\"After SQL (node)\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" multiline=\"true\" name=\"afterNode\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Select Yes to read the SQL statement from the file that is specified in the After SQL (node) statement property.\" label=\"Read After SQL (node) statement from file\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"ReadFromFileAfterSQLNode\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"true\" description=\"Abort the job if there is an error executing a command\" label=\"Fail on error\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"FailOnError\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/></Property></Property><Property contexts=\"target\" default=\"0\" deprecated=\"false\" description=\"Determines how records should be ordered across multiple links.\" engines=\"ee\" filterContexts=\"all\" filterEngines=\"all\" hidden=\"false\" inputLinkCountConstraint=\"multiple\" label=\"Record ordering\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" multiline=\"false\" name=\"RecordOrdering\" required=\"false\" scope=\"stage\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">All records</Value><Value code=\"1\">First record</Value><Value code=\"2\">Ordered</Value><Property default=\"false\" description=\"A column to be used for sorting.\" filterContexts=\"all\" filterEngines=\"all\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/RecordOrdering\" filterValue=\"2\" hidden=\"false\" label=\"Key column\" maxOccurs=\"unbounded\" minOccurs=\"1\" multiline=\"false\" name=\"KeyColumn\" required=\"false\" scope=\"stage\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"category\"><Property callout=\"columns\" calloutDescription=\"Choose columns to define cross-link ordering\" calloutLabel=\"Available columns\" calloutType=\"builder\" description=\"The name of a column to be used for sorting.\" filterContexts=\"all\" filterEngines=\"all\" hidden=\"false\" label=\"Column name\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" multiline=\"false\" name=\"ColumnName\" required=\"true\" scope=\"stage\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"string\" xsi:type=\"asc:CalloutProperty\"><CalloutArgument name=\"columnSelection\">commonInput</CalloutArgument></Property><Property default=\"0\" description=\"Specifies whether sorting should be in ascending or descending order.\" filterContexts=\"all\" filterEngines=\"all\" hidden=\"false\" label=\"Sort order\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" multiline=\"false\" name=\"SortOrder\" required=\"false\" scope=\"stage\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Ascending</Value><Value code=\"1\">Descending</Value></Property><Property default=\"0\" description=\"Specifies whether null values should appear before or after non-null values.\" filterContexts=\"all\" filterEngines=\"all\" hidden=\"false\" label=\"Null order\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" multiline=\"false\" name=\"NullOrder\" required=\"false\" scope=\"stage\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Before</Value><Value code=\"1\">After</Value></Property><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Specifies whether strings should be compared using a case sensitive or insensitive comparison.\" filterContexts=\"all\" filterEngines=\"all\" hidden=\"false\" label=\"Case sensitive\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" multiline=\"false\" name=\"CaseSensitive\" required=\"false\" scope=\"stage\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"bool\"/></Property></Property><Property default=\"2\" description=\"Specifies the type of reoptimization that is done by DB2.\" label=\"Reoptimization\" name=\"ReOptimization\" required=\"false\" scope=\"stage\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"2\">None</Value><Value code=\"3\">Once</Value><Value code=\"4\">Always</Value></Property><Property default=\"1\" description=\"Specifies the lock wait strategy that is used when a lock cannot be obtained immediately.\" filterChildPropertiesOnValue=\"3\" filterContexts=\"target\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/WriteMode\" filterValue=\"0 1 2 3 4 5 7 8\" label=\"Lock wait mode\" name=\"LockWaitMode\" required=\"false\" scope=\"stage\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Return an SQLCODE and SQLSTATE</Value><Value code=\"1\">Use the lock timeout database configuration parameter</Value><Value code=\"2\">Wait indefinitely</Value><Value code=\"3\">User specified</Value><Property description=\"Time to wait for a lock\" label=\"Lock wait time\" maxValue=\"32767\" minValue=\"1\" name=\"LockWaitModeTime\" required=\"true\" type=\"int\"/></Property><Property contexts=\"target request\" description=\"Specifies the pad character that is used in the WHERE clause for string columns that are smaller than the column size.\" label=\"Pad character\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"PadCharacter\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property contexts=\"target\" default=\"false\" description=\"By default the connector runs one player process per database partition. If you want to force the connector to run fewer player processes, set this property to Yes\" engines=\"ee\" filterChildPropertiesOnValue=\"true\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/WriteMode\" filterValue=\"6\" label=\"Limit parallelism\" name=\"LimitParallelism\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"><Property contexts=\"target\" description=\"The total number of player processes across all processing nodes.\" label=\"Total number of player processes\" minValue=\"1\" name=\"PlayerProcessLimit\" required=\"true\" type=\"int\"/></Property><Property contexts=\"target\" default=\"false\" description=\"Determines whether the target table is on DB2 for z/OS.\" filterChildPropertiesOnValue=\"true\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/WriteMode\" filterValue=\"6\" label=\"Bulk load to DB2 on z/OS\" name=\"LoadToZOS\" required=\"false\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"bool\"><Property default=\"0\" description=\"Load method to be used for loading input data into DB2 for z/OS.\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/LoadToZOS/Transfer/TransferType\" filterValue=\"0\" label=\"Load method\" name=\"LoadMethod\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">MVS dataset(s)</Value><Value code=\"1\">Batch pipe(s)</Value><Value code=\"2\">USS pipe(s)</Value></Property><Property description=\"Transfer properties\" label=\"Transfer\" name=\"Transfer\" required=\"false\" type=\"category\"><Property default=\"0\" description=\"Determines the method of transferring data to the z/OS machine.\" label=\"Transfer type\" name=\"TransferType\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">ftp</Value><Value code=\"1\">sftp</Value></Property><Property description=\"Name of the target machine to which the data is sent.\" label=\"Transfer to\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"TransferTo\" required=\"true\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Determines the user name for transferring.\" label=\"User\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"User\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Determines the password for transferring.\" label=\"Password\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"Password\" required=\"false\" type=\"protectedstring\"/><Property description=\"The presence of this option indicates that HFS files is to be used and gives the directory name where the files will be created.  The value should be a fully qualified HFS directory name.\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/LoadToZOS/Transfer/TransferType\" filterValue=\"1\" label=\"HFS file directory\" maxLength=\"512\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"USSFileDirectory\" required=\"true\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"User-entered command sent just before data transfer begins.  FTP example:  quote site vcount=7 datakeepalive=60\" label=\"Transfer command\" maxLength=\"2000\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"TransferCmd\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property default=\"true\" description=\"Select Yes to try to establish a connection again when the initial attempt to connect is unsuccessful.\" filterChildPropertiesOnValue=\"true\" label=\"Retry on connection failure\" name=\"RetryConnection\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"><Property default=\"3\" description=\"Enter the number of times to try to establish a connection after a failure on the initial attempt.\" label=\"Number of retries\" maxValue=\"999999999\" minValue=\"1\" name=\"RetryCount\" required=\"true\" type=\"int\"/><Property default=\"10\" description=\"Enter the time in seconds to wait between retries to establish a connection.\" label=\"Interval between retries\" maxValue=\"999999999\" minValue=\"1\" name=\"RetryInterval\" required=\"true\" type=\"int\"/></Property></Property><Property description=\"This option identifies a prefix to be used when creating MVS dataset names.  If omitted, the transfer user name is used.\" label=\"DSN prefix\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"DSNPrefix\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"If the data is to be transferred to a Batch pipes system on z/OS, this option identifies its name.\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/LoadToZOS/LoadMethod\" filterValue=\"1\" label=\"Batch pipe system ID\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"BatchPipeSystemID\" required=\"true\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"The presence of this option indicates that USS piping is to be used and gives the directory name where the pipes will be created.  The value should be a fully qualified USS directory name.\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/LoadToZOS/LoadMethod\" filterValue=\"2\" label=\"USS pipe directory\" maxLength=\"512\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"USSPipeDirectory\" required=\"true\" type=\"string\"/><Property default=\"false\" description=\"LOAD will not actually be executed, only MVS datasets are created.\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/LoadToZOS/LoadMethod\" filterValue=\"0\" label=\"File(s) only\" name=\"FilesOnly\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"SYSDA\" description=\"This option specifies the device type to be used for various datasets that the LOAD utility may need.  If omitted, the default is SYSDA.\" label=\"Device type\" maxLength=\"8\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"DeviceType\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"If this option is present, then only the indicated partition will be loaded.  If this option is omitted, all partitions of the DB2 for z/OS database table will be loaded.\" label=\"Partition number\" minValue=\"1\" name=\"PartitionNumber\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"/><Property default=\"1000\" description=\"This option specifies an estimated count of the total number of rows to be loaded into all partitions combined.  This estimate is used to calculate the amount of disk space which will be needed on z/OS for various datasets.  If not present, a row estimate of 1000 is used.\" label=\"Row count estimate\" minValue=\"0\" name=\"RowCountEstimate\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"/><Property default=\"0\" description=\"This option requests that statistics be displayed at the end of the load.\" label=\"Statistics\" name=\"Statistics\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">None</Value><Value code=\"1\">All</Value><Value code=\"2\">Index</Value><Value code=\"3\">Table</Value></Property><Property default=\"DB2ZLOAD\" description=\"This is a unique identifier within DB2 for the execution of the LOAD utility.  The default value is DB2ZLOAD.\" label=\"Utility ID\" maxLength=\"16\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"UtilityID\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Indicates whether logging is to occur during the load process.\" label=\"Load with logging\" name=\"LoadWithLogging\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Specifies whether or not the table space is set to the copy-pending status.  (Applicable only when Load with logging = No)\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/LoadToZOS/LoadWithLogging\" filterValue=\"false\" label=\"Set copy-pending\" name=\"SetCopyPending\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"0\" description=\"Specifies the input dataset encoding\" label=\"Encoding\" name=\"Encoding\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">EBCDIC</Value><Value code=\"1\">ASCII</Value><Value code=\"2\">UNICODE</Value><Value code=\"3\">CCSID</Value><Property description=\"The IANA character set name for the encoding.  If not specified, ibm-1047-s390 will be used for EBCDIC, ASCII for ASCII, and UTF-16BE for UNICODE.\" label=\"Character set\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"CharacterSet\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"The IANA character set name for the graphic encoding.  If not specified, UTF-16BE is the default.\" label=\"Graphic character set\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"GraphicCharacterSet\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the coded character set identifier (CCSID) for SBCS data, Mixed data, and DBCS data in the input file.\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/LoadToZOS/Encoding\" filterValue=\"3\" label=\"CCSID\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"CCSID\" required=\"true\" type=\"string\"/></Property><Property default=\"0\" description=\"Specifies whether to run an Image-copy function after Load\" filterChildPropertiesOnValue=\"1 2 3\" label=\"Image-copy function\" name=\"ImageCopyFunction\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">No</Value><Value code=\"1\">Full</Value><Value code=\"2\">Concurrent</Value><Value code=\"3\">Incremental</Value><Property default=\"0\" description=\"Scope of the image-copy\" label=\"Scope\" name=\"Scope\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Full</Value><Value code=\"1\">Single partition</Value></Property><Property description=\"Image-copy file attributes\" label=\"Image-copy file\" name=\"ImageCopyFile\" required=\"false\" type=\"category\"><Property description=\"Dataset name used by the Load utility.\" label=\"Dataset name\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"DatasetName\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the number of buffers to use\" label=\"Number of buffers\" maxValue=\"99\" minValue=\"1\" name=\"NumberOfBuffers\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the device number, device type (generic), or group name for the data set.\" label=\"Unit\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"Unit\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the SMS data class.  The name must be a valid SMS data class and must not exceed 8 characters in length.\" label=\"Data class\" maxLength=\"8\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"DataClass\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the SMS management class.  The name must be a valid SMS management class and must not exceed 8 characters in length.\" label=\"Management class\" maxLength=\"8\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"ManagementClass\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the SMS storage class.  The name must be a valid SMS storage class and must not exceed 8 characters in length.\" label=\"Storage class\" maxLength=\"8\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"StorageClass\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Specifies a list of volume serial numbers for this allocation.  The value should be a string value or a comma-separated list of string values.  The value or list of values may be entered by the user with or without enclosing parentheses.  In the TEMPLATE statement, however, the parentheses are required.  So, if the user does not enter them, the syntax generator should add them.\" label=\"Volume(s)\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"Volumes\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"File disposition properties\" filterProperty=\"/Usage/LoadToZOS/LoadMethod\" filterValue=\"0\" label=\"File disposition\" name=\"FileDisposition\" required=\"false\" type=\"category\"><Property default=\"0\" description=\"This option specifies the disposition status of the dataset(s) used by the LOAD utility.\" label=\"Status\" name=\"Status\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Replace</Value><Value code=\"1\">New</Value><Value code=\"2\">Old</Value><Value code=\"3\">Share</Value><Value code=\"4\">Append</Value></Property><Property default=\"2\" description=\"This option specifies the normal termination disposition of the dataset(s) used by the LOAD utility.\" label=\"Normal termination\" name=\"NormalTermination\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Keep</Value><Value code=\"1\">Delete</Value><Value code=\"2\">Catalog</Value><Value code=\"3\">Uncatalog</Value></Property><Property default=\"2\" description=\"This option specifies the abnormal termination disposition of the dataset(s) used by the LOAD utility.\" label=\"Abnormal termination\" name=\"AbnormalTermination\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Keep</Value><Value code=\"1\">Delete</Value><Value code=\"2\">Catalog</Value><Value code=\"3\">Uncatalog</Value></Property></Property><Property default=\"0\" description=\"Specifies the z/OS disk space allocation unit type\" label=\"Spac